      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻击</span><br>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/19/157749474/47817b4476bcd8b44c86c87debf042f2_2739674522628291997.png",
                "id": "talent53472",
                "key": "波刃锋斩",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "波刃锋斩"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span><br>造成2点<span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">水元素伤害</span>，然后<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">准备技能：涟锋旋刃</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">涟锋旋刃</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成1点<span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">水元素伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/19/157749474/09d978772c4b7b95a9b3896de9e32f9a_5462094408998696763.png",
                "id": "talent28395",
                "key": "洄涡锋刃",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "洄涡锋刃"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成3点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素伤害</span>。在对方场上生成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">暗流的诅咒</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">暗流的诅咒</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所在阵营的角色使用元素战技或元素爆发时：</span>需要多花费1个元素骰。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/19/157749474/d93cfa2833ead49715475616489de21c_2708211077912585703.png",
                "id": "talent15373",
                "key": "激流强震",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "激流强震"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被动技能</span></p><p>【被动】战斗开始时，初始附属<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">水之新生</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">水之新生</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态<br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附属角色被击倒时：</span>移除此效果，使角色<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">免于被击倒</span>，并治疗该角色到4点生命值。此效果触发后，角色造成的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>变为<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素伤害</span>，且<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素伤害</span>+1。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/19/157749474/1bbe84955410406904930648b9a4dd36_7964348554076713627.png",
                "id": "talent81900",
                "key": "水之新生",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "水之新生"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着水元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">蒸发</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">感电</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">冻结</span>：本伤害+1，使目标本回合无法行动（受到物理或火元素伤害后提前解除，但是伤害+2）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">绽放</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下次火/雷伤害+2的[<span style=\"color: white\">草原核</span>]</p><p><strong><span style=\"color: white\">草原核</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span></p><p>我方对敌方出战角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>时，伤害值+2。</p><p><span style=\"color: white\">可用次数：1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/19/157749474/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_2046695583563147915.png",
                "id": "talent99464",
                "key": "水元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "水元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备技能</span></strong><br>有些技能无法被直接使用，而是需要一定次数的行动轮来进行<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>。</p><p>轮到一位牌手行动时，如果该牌手的「出战角色」正在<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>技能，则跳过该牌手的行动：如果技能已经完成<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>，角色将会在此时直接使用此技能。（此类需要<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>的技能，无法触发「使用技能后」」「角色引发元素反应后」效果。）</p><p>只有「出战角色」才能<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>技能；如果正在<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>技能的「出战角色」被切换到后台，技能的<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>就会被打断。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数<br></span></strong>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">免于被击倒</span></strong></p><p>一些效果会使角色在生命值被降为0的时候<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">免于被击倒</span>，并治疗该角色到一定生命值。</p><p>此时，角色不视为被<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">击倒</span>过。（因此，角色所附属的装备和状态不会被弃置，充能也不会被清空。）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/19/157749474/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_466274761421134646.png",
